.el .ds Aq '
.TH background-agent 1  "background-agent " 
.SH NAME
background\-agent \- Legacy alias for task management
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBbackground\-agent\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBbackground\-agent\fR is a compatibility alias for the canonical \fBtask\fR
command group. Use \fBtask\fR in new scripts, documentation, and operator
workflows.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
task(1)
Canonical task management command reference
.SH COMPATIBILITY
Existing invocations such as \fBrestflow background\-agent list\fR continue to
parse, but behavior and help are owned by \fBtask\fR.
